    "203675070": {
      "title": "Localization algorithm based on analysis of RSSI error for Wireless Sensor Networks",
      "abstract": "A new localization algorithm for Wireless Sensor Networks(WSN) is proposed in this paper.The new algorithm can handle some problems of WSN.The two key factors that result in error of distance measurement by RSSI are analyzed in this paper.In order to reduce the RSSI error,the parameters are amended online with three network nodes.The simulation results show that the algorithm is effective."
